# Phase 2 Implementation Plan — LoanPro 2025

Building on completed Phase 1 (AdMob ads + local coin system). Phase 2 adds user accounts, cloud persistence, saved calculations, and a pro subscription tier.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Supabase Project**: You'll need to create a Supabase project at [supabase.com](https://supabase.com) to get the project URL and anon key. I'll use placeholders during development.

> [!WARNING]
> **Apple Developer Account**: Sign in with Apple requires an active Apple Developer membership and App ID configuration with the "Sign In with Apple" capability enabled.

> [!CAUTION]
> **Breaking change to CoinManager**: Phase 2 migrates coin storage from UserDefaults → Supabase. Existing users' coins will be preserved via a one-time migration on first sign-in. If they never sign in, coins stay local.

