## Milestone 1 — Supabase Authentication

### Infrastructure

#### [NEW] `Services/SupabaseManager.swift`
- Supabase Swift client initialization with project URL + anon key
- Shared singleton for all Supabase operations
- Session management (auto-refresh, token storage)

#### [NEW] `Services/AuthService.swift`
- Sign in with Apple (using `ASAuthorizationController`)
- Sign in with Google (using Google Sign-In SDK)
- Email/Password sign up + sign in
- Sign out, delete account
- `@Published var currentUser: User?`
- `@Published var isAuthenticated: Bool`
- Guest mode: all features work without auth, data stays local

### UI Components

#### [NEW] `Views/Auth/SignInView.swift`
- Premium login screen with app branding
- Three sign-in buttons: Apple (black), Google (white), Email (indigo)
- "Continue as Guest" option at the bottom
- Animated background consistent with app theme

#### [NEW] `Views/Auth/EmailAuthView.swift`
- Email + password form (sign up / sign in toggle)
- Input validation, error display
- "Forgot Password" flow via Supabase magic link

#### [NEW] `Views/Profile/ProfileView.swift`
- User avatar, name, email display
- Sign-out button
- "Delete Account" (with confirmation)
- Coin balance (synced)
- Saved calculations count
- Pro status badge
- Accessible from Settings

### Modified Files

#### [MODIFY] [LoanPro2025App.swift](file:///Users/inkalvadodariya/loan_calculator/loan_calculator/App/LoanPro2025App.swift)
