## Milestone 4 — Pro Tier (Subscription)

### StoreKit Integration

#### [NEW] `Services/StoreKitManager.swift`
- StoreKit 2 API for subscription management
- Products: `loanpro_monthly` ($2.99/mo), `loanpro_yearly` ($19.99/yr)
- `@Published var isPro: Bool`
- Receipt validation via Supabase Edge Function
- Restore purchases support

#### [NEW] `Views/Pro/ProUpgradeView.swift`
- Premium paywall screen with feature comparison
- Free vs Pro feature table
- Subscription pricing cards (monthly/yearly with savings badge)
- "Restore Purchases" link
- Terms of service / privacy policy links (required by App Store)

### Pro Features

| Feature | Free Users | Pro Users |
|---|---|---|
| All calculators | ✅ | ✅ |
| Banner ads | Shown | **Hidden** |
| Native ads | Shown | **Hidden** |
| Interstitial ads | Shown | **Hidden** |
| PDF/CSV export | Costs coins | **Free (unlimited)** |
| Full amortization | Watch reward ad | **Always unlocked** |
| Saved calculations | Up to 5 | **Unlimited** |
| Calculation history | Last 10 | **Unlimited** |
| Dark mode | ✅ | ✅ |
| Priority support | ❌ | ✅ |

### Modified Files

#### [MODIFY] [AdService.swift](file:///Users/inkalvadodariya/loan_calculator/loan_calculator/Services/AdService.swift)
- Check `StoreKitManager.shared.isPro` before loading/showing any ad
- If pro → skip all ad loading entirely (saves bandwidth)

#### [MODIFY] [CoinManager.swift](file:///Users/inkalvadodariya/loan_calculator/loan_calculator/Services/CoinManager.swift)
- If pro → bypass coin checks on export (always allow)

#### [MODIFY] [ResultsView.swift](file:///Users/inkalvadodariya/loan_calculator/loan_calculator/Views/Results/ResultsView.swift)
- If pro → hide reward ad button, show amortization directly
- If pro → remove coin cost labels from export menu

#### [MODIFY] [SettingsView.swift](file:///Users/inkalvadodariya/loan_calculator/loan_calculator/Views/Main/SettingsView.swift)
