## Dependencies to Add

| Package | Purpose | Method |
|---|---|---|
| `supabase-swift` | Auth + Database + Realtime | SPM: `https://github.com/supabase/supabase-swift` |
| `GoogleSignIn-iOS` | Google sign-in | SPM: `https://github.com/google/GoogleSignIn-iOS` |

Apple Sign In uses native `AuthenticationServices` framework (no external dependency).

---

## Verification Plan

### Milestone 1 (Auth)
- Sign in with all 3 methods → verify user created in Supabase dashboard
- Sign out → verify session cleared
- Guest mode → verify all calculator features still work
- Kill app → reopen → verify session persists

### Milestone 2 (Cloud Sync)
- Sign in → verify coin balance syncs to Supabase
- Earn coins → verify cloud balance updates
- Sign in on hypothetical second device → verify same balance
- Go offline → earn coins → go online → verify sync

### Milestone 3 (Saved Calcs)
- Save 3 calculations → verify they appear in History
- Delete one → verify removal
- Tap a saved calc → verify it restores inputs and navigates to results
- Search/filter → verify correct results

### Milestone 4 (Pro)
- Purchase subscription (sandbox) → verify ads disappear
- Export PDF/CSV → verify no coin cost
- Cancel subscription → verify ads return
- Restore purchases → verify pro status restored

### Milestone 5 (UX)
- Toggle dark mode → verify all screens render correctly
- Complete 3 calculations → verify rate prompt appears
- Fresh install → verify onboarding carousel appears once
